data.description: Welcome to the serene community of Kitsap Lake! This beautifully designed 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom 2 car garage residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Well-maintained home with lush, landscaped front yard. Fully fenced low maintenance backyard. Gardening space across the driveway. The main level open concept floor plan creates an ideal atmosphere for entertaining from any space. Spacious laundry room. The kitchen boasts everything you need. 2nd floor offers 3 bedrooms, guest bath, including Master suite w/ walk-in closet and en-suite bath and a versatile bonus room. 1mile from Kitsap Lake boat launch. Great location close to the surrounding bases, ferry, shopping, dining, and highways for easy commute.
